qas.question: What cruise line has its headquarters in Southampton?
Besides Carnival, what other major cruise line parks its record-breaking cruise ships in Southampton Water?
In addition to P&O Cruises and Cunard Line, what other brand does Carnival Corporation own?

context: Many of the world's largest cruise ships can regularly be seen in Southampton water, including record-breaking vessels from <a1_0>Royal Caribbean<a1_0/> and <a0_0>Carnival Corporation & plc<a0_0/>. The latter has headquarters in Southampton, with its brands including <a2_0>Princess Cruises<a2_0/>, P&O Cruises and Cunard Line.
